Created attachment 180958
cad/freecad port update

* Remove obsolete cmake pivy option;
* Fix line separators in source and data files;
* Build with fortran support, which is required for some of FreeCAD
  modules:
    /lib/libgcc_s.so.1: version GCC_4.6.0 required by
      /usr/local/lib/gcc49/libgfortran.so.3 not found
* Add option to import collada files;
* Update to 20170310 snapshot.
